{"lemma":"جَهْدُ","slug":"جَهْدُ","root":"ج.ه.د","root_slug":"ج-ه-د","root_link":"/words/roots/ج-ه-د","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"جَهْد","root":"جهد","pos":"N","occurrence_count":5},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":7},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n6512","n6515","n6516"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AC%D9%8E%D9%87%D9%92%D8%AF%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to strive, to struggle, to labour, to exert oneself, to take pains, to endeavor (especially in the sense of strenuously, to the utmost of one's ability, etc.)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to overwork, to overtax, to fatigue, to exhaust","tags":["transitive"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of جَهَدَ (jahada) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"labour, toil, exertion, effort"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"strain, exertion, effort"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"power, ability"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"to the limit of, as much as (جُهْدَ (juhda) used as preposition)","examples":[{"text":"هُوَ أَكَلَ جُهْدَ طَاقَتِهِ.","english":"He ate to the limit of his ability."}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/d͡ʒa.ha.da/","/d͡ʒahd/","/d͡ʒuhd/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n6512","headword_ar":"جَهَدَ","root":"jhd","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, L, &c.,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahodN","text_ar":"جَهْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He strove, laboured,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"toiled; exerted himself"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his power"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"efforts"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"endeavours"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ability; employed himself vigorously, strenuously, laboriously, diligently, studiously, sedulously, earnestly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with energy; was diligent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"studious; took pains,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extraordinary pains;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, L, K;)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY ka*aA","text_ar":"فِى كَذَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in such a thing;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S;) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY AlA^amori","text_ar":"فِى الاَمْرِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the affair;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ajthd","text_ar":"اجتهد","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (A, K;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jAhd","text_ar":"جاهد","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", with respect to speech and actions: (L:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahada fiY AlA^amori","text_ar":"جَهَدَ فِى الاَمْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor. and inf. n. as above,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he did his utmost,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"used his utmost power"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"efforts"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"endeavours"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ability, in prosecuting the affair:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ajthd","text_ar":"اجتهد","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tjAhd","text_ar":"تجاهد","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he exerted unsparingly his power,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ability:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY AlA^amori","text_ar":"فِى الاَمْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ajthd","text_ar":"اجتهد","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he exerted unsparingly his power,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ability, in the prosecution of the affair, so as to effect his utmost."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aijohado jahadaka fiY h*aA AlA^amori","text_ar":"اِجْهَدْ جَهَدَكَ فِى هذَا الاَمْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Do thine utmost in this affair:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Fr, S, K: *) but not"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juhodaka","text_ar":"جُهْدَكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Fr, S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raA^oyahu","text_ar":"رَاْيَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ajthd","text_ar":"اجتهد","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He took pains,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"put himself to trouble"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fatigue, to form a right judgment"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"opinion."},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raA^oyiY wanafosiY Hat~aY","text_ar":"رَاْيِى وَنَفْسِى حَتَّى"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aijotahadotu","text_ar":"اِجْتَهَدْتُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balagotu majohuwdiY","text_ar":"بَلَغْتُ مَجْهُودِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I exerted my judgment and my mind so that I attained the utmost of my power,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ability."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, L.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahadabihi","text_ar":"جَهَدَبِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He tried, proved,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"examined, him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eani Alxayori wa gayorihi","text_ar":"عَنِ الخَيْرِ وَ غَيْرِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"respecting good"},{"kind":"text","text":"qualities, &c.]. (L.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahadahu","text_ar":"جَهَدَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh, L, Msb,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh, L,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahodN","text_ar":"جَهْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(an affair, and a disease,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affected him severely; harassed, embarrassed, distressed, afflicted, troubled, inconvenienced, fatigued,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wearied, him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it"},{"kind":"text","text":"(disease, L and K, and fatigue, and love, L)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rendered him lean; emaciated him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he burdened him beyond his power; imposed upon him that which was beyond his power;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ajhdhu","text_ar":"اجهدهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Mgh:) and, [as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ajhdhu","text_ar":"اجهدهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he importuned him, harassed him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plied him hard, in asking, begging,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"petitioning."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juhida","text_ar":"جُهِدَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", said of a man,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was severely affected, harassed, embarrassed, distressed, afflicted, troubled, inconvenienced, fatigued,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wearied:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was grieved,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made sorry"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unhappy."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSaAbahumo quHuwTN mina AlmaTari fajuhiduwA jahodFA $adiydFA","text_ar":"اَصَابَهُمْ قُحُوطٌ مِنَ المَطَرِ فَجُهِدُوا جَهْدًا شَدِيدًا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Drought befell them, and they consequently became severely distressed."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juhiduwA","text_ar":"جُهِدُوا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They were,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, afflicted with drought, barrenness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dearth;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with drought, and dryness of the earth."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajulN yajohadu A^ano yaHomila silaAHahu","text_ar":"رَجُلٌ يَجْهَدُ اَنْ يَحْمِلَ سِلَاحَهُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mina AlD~aEofi","text_ar":"مِنَ الضَّعْفِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yajohadu nafosahu","text_ar":"يَجْهَدُ نَفْسَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A man who imposes upon himself a difficulty,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"trouble,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fatigue,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a difficult"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"severe task,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who strains,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strains himself, in the carrying of his weapons,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"arms, by reason of weakness."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahada daAb~atahu","text_ar":"جَهَدَ دَابَّتَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AjhdhA","text_ar":"اجهدها","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He jaded, harassed, distressed, fatigued,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wearied, his beast; i. q."},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaga jahodahaA","text_ar":"بَلَغَ جَهْدَهَا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he tasked,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plied, his beast beyond his power in journeying,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"marching,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in respect of pace."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajohadotuhu EalaY A^ano yafoEala","text_ar":"اَجْهَدْتُهُ عَلَى اَنْ يَفْعَلَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ka*aA wa ka*aA","text_ar":"كَذَا وَ كَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I importuned him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"harassed him, to do such and such things"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (L.) ―         -b2-  Also, (S, Msb,) aor. as above, (A,) and so the inf. n., (Msb,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He deprived it"},{"kind":"text","text":"(namely, milk,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of its butter,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"entirely:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"churned it so as to extract its butter and render it sweet and pleasant:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mixed it with water:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"diluted it so that it consisted for the most part of water:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and in like manner it  is used in relation to broth. (A.) ―         -b3-  Hence, (Msb,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahadahaA","text_ar":"جَهَدَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He lay with her;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"compressed her:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, Msb, from a trad.:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafaEahaA","text_ar":"دَفَعَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HafazahaA","text_ar":"حَفَزَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which has a similar meaning]. (L.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahada AlT~aEaAmi","text_ar":"جَهَدَ الطَّعَامِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He desired the food eagerly; longed for it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ajhdhu","text_ar":"اجهدهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juhida AlT~aEaAmu","text_ar":"جُهِدَ الطَّعَامُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ujohida","text_ar":"اُجْهِدَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The food was eagerly desired,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"longed for."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) ―         -b5-  Also (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He ate much of the food:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he left nothing of it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*aA","text_ar":"هٰذَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kalaA^N yajohaduhu AlmaAlu","text_ar":"كَلَاٌ يَجْهَدُهُ المَالُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"This is herbage,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pasture, of which the cattle eat perseveringly."},{"kind":"text","text":"(AA, TA.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahida","text_ar":"جَهِدَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a state of life)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, hard, difficult, strait,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"distressful."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.)"}],"source_refs":["K","TA","L","Msb","S","A","Mgh"]},{"entry_id":"n6515","headword_ar":"جَهْدٌ","root":"jhd","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Power; ability;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juhodN","text_ar":"جُهْدٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, A, IAth, L, Msb, K;) the latter of the dial. of El- Hijáz, and the former of other dials.; (Msb;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majohuwdN","text_ar":"مَجْهُودٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (A:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jhd","text_ar":"جهد"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the Kur ix. 80 is read both"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahod","text_ar":"جَهْد"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juhd","text_ar":"جُهد","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahodN","text_ar":"جَهْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"labour, toil, exertion, effort, endeavour, energy, diligence, painstaking,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extraordinary painstaking:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L: [see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahada","text_ar":"جَهَدَ"},{"kind":"text","text":":]) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juhodN","text_ar":"جُهْدٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"has the signification first mentioned above, (Fr, S, IAth, Msb,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahodN","text_ar":"جَهْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with fet-h, is from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aijohado jahodaka","text_ar":"اِجْهَدْ جَهْدَكَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY h`*aA AlA^amori","text_ar":"فِى هٰذَا الاَمْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Fr, S,) or from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahada fiY AlA^amori","text_ar":"جَهَدَ فِى الاَمْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", being an inf. n. from this verb, (Msb,) and signifies, [as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majohuwdN","text_ar":"مَجْهُودٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":",] one's"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"utmost;"},{"kind":"text","text":"the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"utmost of one's power"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ability"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"efforts"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"endeavours"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"energy."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Fr, S, IAth, Msb, K.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ba*ala Aljahoda","text_ar":"بَذَلَ الجَهْدَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"blg","text_ar":"بلغ"},{"kind":"text","text":", &c.,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Almajohuwda","text_ar":"المَجْهُودَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahodahu","text_ar":"جَهْدَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh,) [and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majohuwdahu","text_ar":"مَجْهُودَهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He exerted unsparingly his power"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ability:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) [or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his utmost power"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ability"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"efforts"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"endeavours"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"energy;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as shown above.] And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaga","text_ar":"بَلَغَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahodahu","text_ar":"جَهْدَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, L,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majohuwdahu","text_ar":"مَجْهُودَهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He accomplished the utmost of his power"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ability; did his utmost."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, L. [Like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahada jahodahu","text_ar":"جَهَدَ جَهْدَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaga jahoda daAb~atihi","text_ar":"بَلَغَ جَهْدَ دَابَّتِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", below.]) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juhayodaY","text_ar":"جُهَيْدَى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahodN","text_ar":"جَهْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) as in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA^abolugan~a juhayodaAYa","text_ar":"لَاَبْلُغَنَّ جُهَيْدَاىَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY AlA^amori","text_ar":"فِى الاَمْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, TK,) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I will assuredly accomplish the utmost of my power,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ability, in the affair."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TK. [In a copy of the A,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juhayodaAka","text_ar":"جُهَيْدَاكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and so in the TA, I believe from that same copy.]) [So, too, is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juhaAdaY","text_ar":"جُهَادَى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; as in the saying,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juhaAdaAka","text_ar":"جُهَادَاكَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ano tafoEala","text_ar":"اَنْ تَفْعَلَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The utmost of thy power,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ability,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the utmost of thy case, is,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"will be, thy doing"},{"kind":"text","text":"[such a thing]; syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quSaAraAka","text_ar":"قُصَارَاكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.], (JK, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaAyapu A^amorika","text_ar":"غَايَةُ اَمْرِكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al~a*iyna A^aqosamuwA biA@ll~`hi jahoda","text_ar":"الَّذِينَ اَقْسَمُوا بِا@للّٰهِ جَهْدَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ayomaAnihimo","text_ar":"اَيْمَانِهِمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the Kur [v. 58, &c.], means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Who swore by God with the most energetic of their oaths:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * Jel:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the strongest,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"most forcible, of their oaths;"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jhd","text_ar":"جهد"},{"kind":"text","text":"being originally an inf. n., and in the accus. as a denotative of state with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yajohaduwna","text_ar":"يَجْهَدُونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"understood before it, or as an inf. n. (Bd.) ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Difficulty,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"grievousness; embarrassment, distress, affliction, trouble, inconvenience, fatigue,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"weariness;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, IAth, Mgh, Msb, K;) so accord. to some who say that ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juhodN","text_ar":"جُهْدٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", with damm, has the first of the significations assigned to it above; (Msb;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majohuwdN","text_ar":"مَجْهُودٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Mgh:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a disease,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"difficulty, that distresses"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"afflicts, a man;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juhodN","text_ar":"جُهْدٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (JK.) Hence,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahodu AlbalaA='i","text_ar":"جَهْدُ البَلَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A state of difficulty,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"trouble, to which death is preferred:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"largeness of one's family,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"household, combined with poverty."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K. *) [Hence also,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaga","text_ar":"بَلَغَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahoda daAb~atihi","text_ar":"جَهْدَ دَابَّتِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaga ma$aq~atahaA","text_ar":"بَلَغَ مَشَقَّتَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahadahaA","text_ar":"جَهَدَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":": see 1. (K.) ―         -b3-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Small provision, upon which a man possessing little property can live"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, L)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with difficulty."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahodN Almuqil~i","text_ar":"جَهْدٌ المُقِلِّ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What a man who possesses little property can afford to give in payment of the poor-rate required by the law."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, from a trad.)"}],"source_refs":["A","S","Fr","IAth","Msb","Mgh","L","JK","TK","K"]},{"entry_id":"n6516","headword_ar":"جُهْدٌ","root":"jhd","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahodN","text_ar":"جَهْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in five places.       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Milk mixed"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with water:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majohuwdN","text_ar":"مَجْهُودٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (JK.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]}}